      "title": "Minister Susil to Russia to ask for oil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the Minister of Education Susil Premajayantha is scheduled to go to Russia for discussions on obtaining fuel.",
        "Former Sri Lankan Ambassador to Russia Saman Weerasinghe is also scheduled to leave for Russia with him, government sources said.",
        "Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera also stated at a media briefing yesterday that two Sri Lankan representatives will be leaving for talks with Russia."
      ],
